about.summary: A Python implementation of a kd-tree

name: kdtree
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "kdtree" %}
{% set version = "0.16" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 386df6c7816a05e0fab974e3035df944f99ef68b5615f4a416771391e33d7534

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - kdtree

about:
  home: https://github.com/stefankoegl/kdtree
  license: ISC (ISCL)
  license_family: OTHER
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A Python implementation of a kd-tree
  doc_url: https://python-kdtree.readthedocs.org/
  dev_url: https://github.com/stefankoegl/kdtree

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lincrosenbach
    - kfasolin
    - nicoddemus
